<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٢ - <span class="c2">(١٤٨٠)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7021">يَحْيَى بْنُ يَحْيَى </a>، أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6709">هُشَيْمٌ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1513">حُصَيْنٍ،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1851">وَدَاوُدَ،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6314">وَمُغِيرَةَ،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/644">وَإِسْمَاعِيلَ،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/723">وَأَشْعَثَ </a>، عَنِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٩٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3071">الشَّعْبِيِّ </a>أَنَّهُ قَالَ: دَخَلْتُ عَلَى <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5068">فَاطِمَةَ بِنْتِ قَيْسٍ </a>بِمِثْلِ حَدِيثِ زُهَيْرٍ عَنْ هُشَيْمٍ .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>